    "The background is related to v 2, as determined by the participant geometry, and therefore is the largest with respect to the participant plane ( PP).",
    "The CME-driven charge separation is along the magnetic field direction ( B), unlike PP.",
    "The B and PP are generally correlated with the impact parameter direction, RP, and therefore correlated among themselves.",
